# Config & Environment

## Must
- "12-factor config: read from process.env only in a central config module"
- "Validate required env on startup with a schema (e.g., zod/joi)"
- "Provide .env.example with documented variables: PORT, SESSION_SECRET, CORS_ORIGINS, MYSQL_*, GOOGLE_*"

## Should
- "Set NODE_ENV checks for behavior toggles (e.g., killProcessOnPort only in development)"
